metadata.name: KumaBoss #1
metadata.description:
Kuma Boss is an exclusive collection of 5,555 NFT that enhanced the Alpha Boss sleeping in your soul
There are 4 families conquering Ferratuma land: 
The Zinata family
he Vesamir family
The Tomesh family
The Eclipso family
The torch of war has been lighted up, Big Boss is calling all of you to join and show your strength to the world
